records.Description__c:
Deploy Pardot for common marketing automation use cases including website visitor tracking, landing pages and forms, email campaigns and customer journeys, unsubscribe/preference centre and social message integration. 

- Enable Pardot connection to Salesforce.
- Map Salesforce custom fields to Pardot custom fields.
- Enable Pardot-Salesforce user sync.
- Connect Pardot campaigns to Salesforce campaigns.
- Load Salesforce contacts and leads into Pardot.
- Modify Salesforce lead and contact page layouts to expose Pardot interactions for sales users.
- Provide website script to log visitor activity on website. CREATIVESPARQ will provide the website tracking script. IR Supplies and Services' web team will add the script to all web pages.
- Assist in creating a vanity tracker domain (CNAME) for branded Pardot-hosted links.
- Create 1 landing web form.
- Create 4 email templates.
- Build 1 nurture campaign using Pardot Engagement Studio.
- Configure events and conditions that will push a marketing qualified prospect from Pardot to Salesforce and notify sales representatives to take action.

Note: Client to provide marketing content and branding.
records.Name: Configure Pardot for marketing automation
